## COUNT PAIRS WITH SUM

import java.util.*;

class CountPairs {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int[] arr = {1, 5, 7, -1, 5};
int k = 6;

```
    HashMap<Integer, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();
    int count = 0;

    for (int num : arr) {
        int diff = k - num;

        if (map.containsKey(diff)) {
            count += map.get(diff);
        }

        map.put(num, map.getOrDefault(num, 0) + 1);
    }

    System.out.println(count);
}
```

}

